{
  "name": "Se7enSlasher - code implementation training #2 - bass reset with delay code",
  "description": "",
  "frame_eqs": "timepeak = if(equal(time%0.1, 0),timepeak=timepeak+0.01, timepeak); //the timepeak variable increases using the time variable in sync\n\n\n/////////////TRIGGER OPTION////////////////\n\n//Simple Bass Trigger//\n//timepeak = if(above(bass, 2),timepeak=0, timepeak); //reset the timepeak vaariable if the beat is below 2 (trigger algorithm) (commented this because not necessary)\n\n//Bass Trigger with Delay//\nbassdelay = timepeak>0.5; //declared the another variable with the simple condition\nbeatdelaytrigger = if(bassdelay, if(above(bass, 2), timepeak=0, timepeak), bleh); //another simple declaration, if the beat triggered with the delay above 0.5, it actually resets the timepeak variable to 0.\n\n\nmonitor = timepeak;\nq1=timepeak; //we carry this variable to custom shapes, waves etc.\n\n//for preset testing\ndecay=0;\nwave_a=0;",
